"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israel Defense Forces are trying to stop new missiles from Iran. Saudi Arabia, Qatar, and Bahrain also stopped attacks overnight.\",            \"english_title\": \"Middle East Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las fuerzas de defensa de Israel tratan de parar nuevos misiles de Ir\u00e1n. Arabia Saudita, Catar y Bar\u00e9in tambi\u00e9n pararon ataques en la noche.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tensiones en Medio Oriente\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"China is not directly affected by the war in the Middle East yet, but it is feeling some effects.\",            \"english_title\": \"China Feels War Effects\",            \"translated_version\": \"China no est\u00e1 afectada directamente por la guerra en Medio Oriente todav\u00eda, pero siente algunos efectos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"China siente efectos de guerra\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine's president says Kyiv will help only if it does not weaken its own air defenses.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine's Conditional Help\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania dice que Kyiv ayudar\u00e1 solo si no debilita sus propias defensas a\u00e9reas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ayuda condicional de Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Iranian Kurdish opposition groups in northern Iraq say they have plans to cross the border but have not done so yet.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kurdish Plans\",            \"translated_version\": \"Grupos de oposici\u00f3n kurdos iran\u00edes en el norte de Irak dicen que tienen planes de cruzar la frontera pero no lo han hecho todav\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Planes kurdos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"There are big traffic jams after warnings for people to leave the Hezbollah area, as Israel increases its attacks in Lebanon.\",            \"english_title\": \"Traffic Jams in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay grandes atascos de tr\u00e1fico despu\u00e9s de advertencias para que la gente salga del \u00e1rea de Hezbollah, mientras Israel aumenta sus ataques en L\u00edbano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Atascos en L\u00edbano\"        }    ]}"